{"tid":191942,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【嚴選】香港大學生柒事回顧","createTime":"2017-04-08T08:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T10:27:29.000Z","uid":18650,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"74b753c236e9405aa82bfde5fc8b51496d40bf96","tid":191942,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T08:56:23.000Z","msg":"城大：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20151025/19347090\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20151025%2F19347090&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=b17f9f6a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20151025%2F19347090&h=699669ea\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20151025/19347090</a><br />\n城大學生會商學院及學部聯會主席鄭源霖情緒激動地「反枱」及辱罵台上候選內閣，勒令候選內閣起立接受訓斥，並表示不滿的候選內閣成員的工作表現和態度，辱罵過後亦指令台上的候選內閣叫口號。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n科大：<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170225/19939809\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170225%2F19939809&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=7802e65b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20170225%2F19939809&h=e8db8e61\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20170225/19939809</a><br />\n科技大學5間宿生會去年在校園「叫莊」（Chanting）時爆衝突，一名二年級男生涉推撞兩同學，被控兩項襲擊致造成身體傷害罪。主任裁判官練錦鴻得悉被告是一名學生後揶揄謂：「讀乜嘢？武術呀？」當值律師索取指示後，指被告讀電子工程系。<br />\n<br />\n科大2014年亦曾發生同類事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港大：<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170406/00176_061.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170406%2F00176_061.html&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=4891bd44\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20170406/00176_061.html</a><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">「圍內玩下啫」「傳統文化嚟」</span><br />\n香港大學繼日前爆出學生舍堂二十人向一名聖約翰學院幹事會參選人下體滴蠟的集體欺凌事件後，再爆出有數名疑似港大男生涉在宿舍內，集體性欺凌一名男生！片中一名男生遭數名男生按壓在床上，遭一名身穿印有「CHEMISTRY HKU」（香港大學化學系）上衣的男生，自掏陽具，打向被按壓男生的頭部後方，又不斷搖晃，動作猥瑣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歡迎補充其他事件/其他大學既事件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20863e40dfc392beed3bc5caf53bccaafcb2819c","tid":191942,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T08:58:57.000Z","msg":"陳雲：下體滴蠟，陽具打臉，據說香港大學流出了一些色情虐待其他室友或幹事候選人的新聞。這是殖民地遺留下來的大學用野蠻軍校的作風調教將來的買辦、朋黨，因此，港大特別多朋黨、專門出朋黨，校內、校友之間都有，畢業了幾十年都有，類似兄弟會那種幫會式的惡劣營私、不顧公德的朋黨，在香港的上層形成一個醜陋的利益保護圈。<br />\n<br />\n這些是世上其他大學沒有的。我讀過德國、法國的老牌大學，他們的宿舍和學生會好正經，是培養正直而優秀的國民的地方。<br />\n<br />\n港大這些垃圾作風，純是出自香港的，在舍堂之間一代一代傳下這些類似流氓軍營的惡劣風俗，一些老校友甚至不以為恥，在我面前津津樂道話當年。<br />\n<br />\n這也不是政府教導或威逼出來的，可以說是香港精英階層自發形成的地下文化傳統。大家要正視香港極其醜惡的一面。英國殖民者一離開香港，香港就露出這麼惡俗和惡毒的上層社會，有香港自身的原因。目前在香港社會高層作惡的，都不是共產黨培養出來的人物。講一句極之老實而得罪大家的說話，如果香港交由共產黨全部殖民統治，由黨校出來的京官直接統治香港，而不是由共產黨委託這香港垃圾本土上層社會來雙重剝削，香港會比現在好很多。&mdash;&mdash;德國民俗學家陳雲的評論。德國大學的兄弟會，也是以利劍格鬥鍛煉勇氣而已，並無虐待入會者，見陳雲《留德隨想錄》的親身經歷。"},{"pid":"d5d2564688bebe650c3914cbb07d14acef37975a","tid":191942,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T08:59:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00E2sB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00E2sB.gif&h=78b62c91&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"9635e2cf2f4b89a6358dbb289b41e65415023b8b","tid":191942,"uid":56627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:01:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00E2sB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00E2sB.gif&h=78b62c91&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊大學"},{"pid":"bf886c233b1f83d35cae427f2f309cd57bce33e6","tid":191942,"uid":37136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:02:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00E2sB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00E2sB.gif&h=78b62c91&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60068ceba95849bb0d9b947f20e8251e3b5a78bd","tid":191942,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00E2sB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00E2sB.gif&h=78b62c91&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊大學</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb97769729a8a20c018841d3271436a6ed67f745","tid":191942,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:04:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00E2sB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00E2sB.gif&h=78b62c91&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊大學</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3bcab44ee880ed79a9b2f646fdbb3ee720eef3","tid":191942,"uid":41974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:05:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d1e335615cb736337f964ab317a62cb9e80e777","tid":191942,"uid":14327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T09:09:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/00E2sB.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F00E2sB.gif&h=78b62c91&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n講緊大學</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/n