4%2F882167_7f4662ceeac22f47054e6906b67a1152.mp4&d=Pl33APIo1S6IjQ3qGLZsPY9%2BoveFa0K0Z8Wn6wXPu4k%3D&h=2d1f6ef0\" target=\"_blank\">http://static.hkej.com/hkej/images/2014/08/14/882167_7f4662ceeac22f47054e6906b67a1152.mp4</a></blockquote><br />\n2014年8月12日新生註冊日，理大的不同學生組織為了招攬新生報名參加迎新營，竟在校內起衝突，更揭發有人疑組織「暗O」(未經校方及學生會批准的迎新活動)。<br />\n<br />\n據當晚「理大編委《理大學生報PolyLife》」facebook專頁上傳的影片所見，事發於大學迎新日第二天傍晚時分邵逸夫體育館新生註冊場地出口對開。當時聚集數十名疑似迎新營搞手，築成三道人牆，疑招攬新生參加「暗O」，當時正下着雨，部分人須舉傘擋雨，期間有兩批疑似搞手共逾廿人起哄爭吵，有人更互相推撞及推倒櫈子，場面火爆，有學生恐殃及池魚，紛避開一旁。在場其他人士見狀，立即將雙方分開，事件始平息。"},{"pid":"50c09c2cadcde00e78cc7a9ad2237a2374aca6e8","tid":191942,"uid":18650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:08:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>香港人踩香港人就係呢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閣下有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d161d036e53198846d39ffc53bdc3e0122b254a2","tid":191942,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:10:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人踩香港人就係呢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閣下有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑下算，唔洗做咩list"},{"pid":"fdaec847475e20b82c02e238e833b8b366893592","tid":191942,"uid":77753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:12:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77acf3eb0be54a8153d64bbf67d3c38efc09e802","tid":191942,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-08T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>香港人踩香港人就係呢種<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n閣下有咩高見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n笑下算，唔洗做咩list<br />\n有心有力就整張民建聯柒事表先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c754f5860205ac40639c99c5c9d2d5436e2bddd","tid":191942,"uid":5451